items.name: Disney Wiki
items.title: Disney Wiki
items.headline: Over 23,000 pages and we keep moving forward by editing every day!
items.desc: The Disney Wiki is a collaborative encyclopedia for everything related to Walt Disney and his work. Here you can find, create, and edit articles on Disney theme parks, film companies, television networks, films, and characters. Discover more than ever before about popular franchises through Mickey Mouse, The Lion King, Aladdin, Phineas and Ferb, Gravity Falls, Wreck-It Ralph, The Disney Afternoon, One Saturday Morning, Kingdom Hearts, Pirates of the Caribbean, Marvel Comics, Star Wars and plenty of Pixar favorites!

items.name: Disney Wiki
items.title: Disney Wiki
items.headline: ¡Bienvenidos al mágico mundo de Disney!
items.desc: Disney Wiki es la enciclopedia en español dedicada a la compañía The Walt Disney Company. Es un proyecto que trata de recopilar toda la información referente a sus productos; desde todos sus personajes como Mickey Mouse; e incluyendo películas, series, videojuegos, parques temáticos y merchandising.

items.name: Disney Parks Wiki
items.title: Disney Parks Wiki
items.headline: Be Enchanted by the Disney Parks Wiki!
items.desc: The Disney Parks Wiki is home to hundreds of pages of information on everything about the Walt Disney Parks and Resorts! In 2009, the company's theme parks hosted approximately 119.1 million guests, making Disney Parks the world's most visited theme park company. Parks range from the USA to France, Japan to China, with more parks planned!

items.name: Disney Channel Wiki
items.title: Disney Channel Wiki
items.headline: Disney Channel Wikia
items.desc: Welcome to the Disney Channel Wikia, a wikia all about the Disney Channel! The Disney Channel is an American basic cable and satellite television network, owned by the Disney-ABC Television Group. It has more than 90 kid-driven, family inclusive entertainment channels and/or channel feeds available in over 160 countries and 30 languages! Enter the wiki now to learn more about the programming on the Disney Channel and how you can help the wiki grow!

items.name: Wickedpedia
items.title: Wickedpedia
items.headline: Wickedpedia, the Disney Villains Wiki
items.desc: Welcome, foolish mortals, to Wickedpedia, the wiki about the Disney Villains that anyone can edit, including mere humans like you. Whether you're a fan of Maleficent, Ursula, Scar, or any other villain in the Disney mythology, this is the wiki where you can share your knowledge and passion with your fellow fans. Join us today... if you dare!

items.name: Disney Fairies Wiki
items.title: Disney Fairies Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Disney Fairies Wikia
items.desc: Welcome to the Disney Fairies Wikia! The Disney Fairies Wikia is a comprehensive database dedicated to providing information for fans on anything and everything related to the Disney fairies! The Disney fairies are seen in movies, video games, tv shows, and more! Enter now to learn everything you'd ever want to know about these fairies!

items.title: Disney Fanon Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Disney Fanon Wikia
items.desc: The Disney Fanon Wikia is a community site housing user-created Disney fanon (fake) games. If you like creating Disney fanon, or if you enjoy fanon that others have created, then this is the place for you! Come explore our content and feel free to add your own original content, so long as you don't mess with existing fanon creted by other users. All are welcome!

items.desc:
This wikia is a fan site which aims to provide information on all the different aspects of the Disney's Hercules universe including characters, films and the television series. This being a fan made wikia means that any visitor is free to edit any of the pages.

Hercules (also known as Hercules: The Animated Series) is an animated series based on the 1997 film of the same name and the Greek myth.

items.title: Disney Princess Wiki
items.headline: Learn more about the Disney Princess Wikia
items.desc: At the Disney Princess Wikia community site we dedicated ourselves to being the number one fan resource and site for everything having to do with the various Disney Princesses. We cover them all from Cinderella to Belle to Pocohantas and more. We also provide information about the films and the various princes that also make up the Disney Universe.

items.headline: Disney Fanfiction Wiki
items.desc: The Disney Fan Fiction Wiki features fan stories based on Disney movies that anyone can edit. On this wiki, you can create one Disney fiction/non-fiction story at a time.

items.desc: A Disney Wiki é uma enciclopédia livre, pública e colaborativa para tudo relacionado ao Walt Disney e Disney Corporation: parques temáticos, empresas de cinema, redes de televisão, filmes, personagens e muito mais. items.name: MotorCity Disney XD Wiki
items.title: MotorCity Disney XD Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Motorcity Wiki!
items.desc:
The Motorcity Wiki is a database and community portal for everything Motorcity, an American animated TV series on DisneyXD created by Chris Pyronoski, who's other work includes Metalocalypse and Avatar:The Last Airbender.

The series is set in a fictional, futuristic Detroit, called Detroit Deluxe, which is an elevated metropolis built over the old Detroit. It is owned by evil billionaire Abraham Kane (Mark Hamill) who rules the citizens under strict laws and bans personal freedoms, such as automobile transportation. Kane now faces one last obstacle: a group of hot-rod wielding rebels who call themselves the Burners. Led by Mike Chilton (Reid Scott), the Burners must stop Kane from conquering Detroit’s last oasis of freedom— an subterranean refuge dubbed Motorcity.
